body.h1: PKPD model for clearance of caffeine
body.p: This model is a physiological-base pharmacokinetic model (PBPK) for the absorption, distribution, metabolism and elimination of caffeine encoded in SBML.
body.div: The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort.
This file has been created by Matthias Koenig.
